{"tid":175432,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"徒手格鬥，中國能戰勝泰臣的武術家，大有人在","createTime":"2017-03-27T13:14:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-28T11:16:15.000Z","uid":25345,"like":3,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ae875c375aaf3d417d43e0e74b5cd4537cfb2732","tid":175432,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T13:14:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://cdn.scrapdigest.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/miketyson1.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.scrapdigest.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F11%2Fmiketyson1.jpeg&h=dcd5a6b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20090612/large/12fx101p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20090612%2Flarge%2F12fx101p.jpg&h=4b189849&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n國內武術家不太可能有能擊敗巔峰時期泰森的存在武術注重養生、武術表演倒是花哨。從來沒見過中國人與世界拳王比過武，。其實擂台上的各種規則很大程度上限制了武術的發揮，<br />\n<br />\n中國功夫，放在20世紀40年代以前還有真傢伙，解放後的中國功夫都是來源於京劇，再後來李小龍創截拳道把中國功夫推向了現代搏擊。別說那麼玄乎，每一門搏擊術都有它的優點，如果真要排個先後，截拳道 &gt; 泰拳 &gt; 拳 擊 &gt; 中國功夫（散打）&gt; 跆拳道。而論實用，就普通人最容易掌握和提高，是拳擊。李小龍那樣的人，一百年出不了一個，他是神。但是優秀的拳王，會層出不窮。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n徒手格鬥，中國能戰勝泰森的人，大有人在。拳擊規則的話，中國武術會死得很慘。挑戰泰森的人中國有好幾位吧，段寶華，張宗健，劉綏濱，有功夫的人在顛峰狀態時多少都有點狂，好象曾經有報道記者也問中國第一散打王柳海龍是否願意挑戰泰森何大師只是第一個而已。他們當時的挑戰，我相信都是為了宣傳中國武術在海外的影響力吧狂妄跟一個人的格鬥實力是有關係的，格鬥水平跟一個人的年齡又有很大關係的，拳打少壯啊，現在泰森老了，何大師，段大師，張大師，劉大師也都老了吧柳海龍也退役了，現在武術落寞了，散打王比賽也沒了，武術都變成舞蹈健身養生了，熱血的中國武術高手也少了，泰拳反而在中國橫衝直撞了，時代啊，唉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n泰森個人巔峰時候就不說了，大家都知道他的閃避速度與力量，基本上已經達到了人類的極限，除非國內武術家在力量上不屬於他，在反應上也不輸於他，才有希望在擂台上擊倒他實戰的話，泰森的下盤功夫應該是個弱點。不能否認，世界上任何技擊，實用性都不如拳擊，拳擊更真實，更高效。更是力量與血性的體現"},{"pid":"106b7cdccac0ed32b3c42038ad621c2b02506bdc","tid":175432,"uid":41237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T13:15:10.000Z","msg":"羅莽 羅莽"},{"pid":"2873b53c9fbf565eea12ea5f0fe1b8efa4da26d3","tid":175432,"uid":31017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T13:17:00.000Z","msg":"胡師傅一代宗師<br />\n健心又健身"},{"pid":"e05c8ef6e5ad7bf7eaac02246a83f4d37c8c5d16","tid":175432,"uid":72730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T13:18:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>胡師傅一代宗師<br />\n健心又健身</blockquote><br />\n又黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e94aaaecf34a0ecd27d1524f0fcfef14dc174506","tid":175432,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T13:18:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KgbwxFrone4&amp;feature=youtu.be&amp;t=139\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DKgbwxFrone4%26feature%3Dyoutu.be%26t%3D139&d=S%2FsiG%2FBE2bBILTWTz3VeJjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=a386c033\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KgbwxFrone4&amp;feature=youtu.be&amp;t=139</a><br />\n<br />\n呢拳好恐怖,個收音大聲到,好大聲拍一聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知中呢拳係咩姿味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c5fd4ff23586724cc3fe443b27635617a6735a8","tid":175432,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T13:20:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KgbwxFrone4&amp;feature=youtu.be&amp;t=139\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DKgbwxFrone4%26feature%3Dyoutu.be%26t%3D139&d=S%2FsiG%2FBE2bBILTWTz3VeJjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=a386c033\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KgbwxFrone4&amp;feature=youtu.be&amp;t=139</a><br />\n<br />\n呢拳好恐怖,個收音大聲到,好大聲拍一聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"