=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知中呢拳係咩姿味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個對手d反應好撚假<br />\n<br />\n似做媒/插水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"803fb50a0aa947918d0d9a6d8bfccaf0a76371b6","tid":175432,"uid":84216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T16:26:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">不能否認，世界上任何技擊，實用性都不如拳擊，拳擊更真實，更高效。</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n拳擊既發源根本就係為左打敗對手<br />\n<br />\n唔似其他國家既武術係包含埋哲理係入面<br />\n<br />\n所以拳擊只係需要訓練打敗對手<br />\n唔撚洗聽d乜9前輩，祖先講歷史"},{"pid":"763134a0835aa97307a1d1200413b66f7c4f4b05","tid":175432,"uid":26329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T16:38:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">不能否認，世界上任何技擊，實用性都不如拳擊，拳擊更真實，更高效。</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n拳擊既發源根本就係為左打敗對手<br />\n<br />\n唔似其他國家既武術係包含埋哲理係入面<br />\n<br />\n所以拳擊只係需要訓練打敗對手<br />\n唔撚洗聽d乜9前輩，祖先講歷史</blockquote><br />\n因此除左要打底人 盡可能都要在減底傷害下擊倒對方"},{"pid":"e8aad2ae51a26470684a8f26200d8ab65bc06172","tid":175432,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T16:57:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搵到個夠大隻<br />\n又要走位夠快，又要夠反應<br />\n仲要有力度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過講開又講<br />\n真係好少見華人會有咁既身形</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n骨架唔同,肌肉品質唔同<br />\n黃種人比較難<br />\n佢呢種唔係健美既肌肉,完全係實戰既肌肉<br />\n硬如鋼鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e988e2a16eb0379cb7e26a555b0db7a2bd2c961c","tid":175432,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T16:58:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">不能否認，世界上任何技擊，實用性都不如拳擊，拳擊更真實，更高效。</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n拳擊既發源根本就係為左打敗對手<br />\n<br />\n唔似其他國家既武術係包含埋哲理係入面<br />\n<br />\n所以拳擊只係需要訓練打敗對手<br />\n唔撚洗聽d乜9前輩，祖先講歷史</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n拳擊真係好強大,老實要好打緊係去練拳啦<br />\n我識個fd,練左幾個月拳已經幾好打下<br />\n肯定好過你練幾年國術"},{"pid":"d721bdaa58e0208de54a8fc734bd66ac1b77fd88","tid":175432,"uid":59695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T17:06:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KgbwxFrone4&amp;feature=youtu.be&amp;t=139\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DKgbwxFrone4%26feature%3Dyoutu.be%26t%3D139&d=S%2FsiG%2FBE2bBILTWTz3VeJjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=a386c033\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KgbwxFrone4&amp;feature=youtu.be&amp;t=139</a>&amp;feature=youtu.be&amp;t=139<br />\n<br />\n呢拳好恐怖,個收音大聲到,好大聲拍一聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知中呢拳係咩姿味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個對手d反應好撚假<br />\n<br />\n似做媒/插水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔好衝出黎柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0d9ee082664ba3e45a0ee9071451d4f16b8abd7","tid":175432,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T17:06:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KgbwxFrone4&amp;feature=youtu.be&amp;t=139\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DKgbwxFrone4%26feature%3Dyoutu.be%26t%3D139&d=S%2FsiG%2FBE2bBILTWTz3VeJjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=a386c033\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KgbwxFrone4&amp;feature=youtu.be&amp;t=139</a>&amp;feature=youtu.be&amp;t=139&amp;feature=<a href=\"http://youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be&d=S%2FsiG%2FBE2bBILTWTz3VeJjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3